Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.88,0:00:31.39,ObjectText,,0,0,0,,{\fn7945c739-da34-4855-ad19-aef0f03de57d\fs55\fsp25\fscx90\pos(960,675)}过去决定你的身{\fsp0}姿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.39,0:00:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.03,0:00:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你忘了我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.67,0:00:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.77,0:02:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,什么 彩羽真的失踪了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.16,0:02:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,美冬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.39,0:02:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不论是彩羽的事 还是这次的作战
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.49,0:02:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么都不肯和我们讲真话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.30,0:02:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了又能有什么改变呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.28,0:02:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.14,0:02:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我也曾在对事态了如指掌的时候不知不觉犯下了无可挽回的错误
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.01,0:02:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,早知如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.29,0:03:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,还不如一无所知
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.37,0:03:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.07,0:03:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,本应了解更多的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.43,0:03:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要离开Magius
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.18,0:03:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,莎奈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.60,0:03:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经不想再这样 连家人处于危险之中都不知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.41,0:03:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,即使无法改变命运
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.99,0:03:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不想在这里迎来自己的终结
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.93,0:03:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我也一样 不想在一无所知中任凭彩羽她们消失
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.49,0:03:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.99,0:03:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想和你们一样选择自己的最后时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.22,0:03:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这种事现在选不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.85,0:03:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.57,0:04:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.73,0:04:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.92,0:04:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,回到我们的三日月庄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.37,0:04:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,对了 鹤乃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.65,0:04:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,难道鹤乃她也
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.01,0:04:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,鹤乃还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.23,0:04:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.38,0:04:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.77,0:04:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然事到如今 但鹤乃的事请交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.90,0:04:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定会带她回到三日月庄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.81,0:04:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.79,0:04:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,初 你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.26,0:04:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 这边 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.89,0:04:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,初
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.10,0:04:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,黑江
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.25,0:05:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,初
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.71,0:05:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,音梦和灯花
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.90,0:05:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,就交给姐姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.43,0:05:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,在这神滨 发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.90,0:05:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.61,0:05:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.65,0:05:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.39,0:05:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,还以为心脏要停止跳动了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.49,0:06:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你是那时候的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.46,0:06:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,又见面了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.97,0:06:08.47,ObjectText,,0,0,0,,{\an4\c&H000000&\blur0.8\fs55\b1\pos(634,146)}大型台风「记入史册的风暴」可能导致大范围停电
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.97,0:06:08.47,ObjectText,,0,0,0,,{\an7\c&H1C1DDF&\b1\blur0.8\fs55\bord1\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(1256,398)}保持严正警戒\n强风与高浪可能令人无法站立
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.97,0:06:08.47,ObjectText,,0,0,0,,{\c&H90046A&\b1\fs55\an7\pos(124,126)\blur0.8}避难劝告发布
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.08,0:06:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 那个叫Magius的集团
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.45,0:06:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,将魔女召唤来了神滨吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.58,0:06:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,对 她们想利用大量的魔法少女
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.71,0:06:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,引发分裂与混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.44,0:06:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.25,0:06:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都被骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.56,0:06:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Magius声称只要臣服于自己
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.32,0:06:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,就能避免变成魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.51,0:06:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,真的不会变成魔女吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.78,0:06:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那是逃避魔法少女责任的 懦夫的妄言罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.50,0:06:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我们愿望的代价
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.77,0:06:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么可能这么廉价
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.52,0:06:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,彩羽 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.51,0:06:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.22,0:06:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在大概在Magius的游乐园
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.19,0:07:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,姑且算是没事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.31,0:07:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,但有些危险
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.64,0:07:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,魔女聚集得越来越多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.19,0:07:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我和黑江还在中途分开了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.85,0:07:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,小丘比也不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.23,0:07:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,和黑江？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.51,0:07:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,黑江她一定会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.38,0:07:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,所以现在必须阻止灯花
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.79,0:07:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了 我也很快…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.40,0:07:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,彩羽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.25,0:07:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,挂断了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.10,0:07:31.31,ObjectText,,0,0,0,,{\pos(947,904)\c&HF5F4E1&\bord2\3c&HF0E576&\fne8c3ef5b-aeec-4581-b2f0-95f21f6f57c8}环彩羽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.10,0:07:31.31,ObjectText,,0,0,0,,{\c&H95ABB9&\fne8c3ef5b-aeec-4581-b2f0-95f21f6f57c8\pos(1320,740)\fs55}游乐园
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.61,0:07:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,彩羽是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.84,0:07:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,对 之前你帮我那时候在一旁的那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.21,0:07:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,她没事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.19,0:07:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,勉勉强强
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.40,0:07:41.40,ObjectText,,0,0,0,,{\an7\p1\pos(784,310)\fad(0,200)}m 0 0 l 1000 0 1000 700 0 700
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.40,0:07:41.40,ObjectText,,0,0,0,,{\an7\c&H70869A&\pos(830,330)\fs55\fne8c3ef5b-aeec-4581-b2f0-95f21f6f57c8\fad(0,200)}夏娃觉醒作战\n\n将半径200KM内的魔女聚集至神滨\n{\fs48\fn296517de-03ee-4d85-952d-bdd9a9363bb8}→召唤魔女的手段不明\n→或许是某人的魔法或是谣的力量\n\n{\fne8c3ef5b-aeec-4581-b2f0-95f21f6f57c8\fs55}Magius似乎将制造出的人工魔女\n称作夏娃（Embryo Eve） \n\n通过吸收聚集来的所有魔女的力量\n夏娃将会觉醒\n使Doppel system扩散到整个地球\n{\fs48\fn296517de-03ee-4d85-952d-bdd9a9363bb8}→详细不明
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.40,0:07:41.40,ObjectText,,0,0,0,,{\fsp20\c&HEEEEEE&\b1\pos(910,210)\fad(0,200)}笔记
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.35,0:07:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不快点的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.38,0:07:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,沙耶加 麻美姐是在Magius吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.42,0:07:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,那么我们的目的地和目标也…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.49,0:07:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,八千代 我们也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.50,0:07:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,差点被巴杀死的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.13,0:08:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,应该没忘记吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.47,0:08:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不仅没忘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.11,0:08:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,现在心里还在瑟瑟发抖呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.21,0:08:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.14,0:08:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我们想帮麻美学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.88,0:08:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,也不能放任聚集魔女的人不管
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.70,0:08:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是一石二鸟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.65,0:08:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,巴学姐也一定会做一样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.21,0:08:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.75,0:08:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们快点终结这场闹剧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.89,0:08:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,看 音梦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.43,0:08:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那些星星之火一般的渺小灵魂们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.52,0:08:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,要从现在开始点燃整个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.97,0:08:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Magius之翼可不是为了你玩火而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.20,0:08:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.32,0:09:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,梓美冬有话对我说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.58,0:09:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,灯花
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.70,0:09:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,现在立刻中止这个计划
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.66,0:09:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不应该把无关的人们卷进来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.98,0:09:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你还是这么温柔 美冬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.33,0:09:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,现在还能把损失控制在最小范围内
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.66,0:09:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 美冬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.87,0:09:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,根本没有无关的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.05,0:09:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,人类的发展是以魔法少女的牺牲交换而来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.23,0:09:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我今后决不允许魔法少女继续毫不自知地作为人类的家畜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.49,0:09:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,看来你没有停止计划的打算
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.12,0:09:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,如果美冬无法理解这个计划而感到迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.25,0:09:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我会替你思考
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.50,0:09:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,替你选择的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.36,0:09:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这样不好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.77,0:09:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我不期望 这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.71,0:10:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,鹤乃 和我一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.20,0:10:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,鹤乃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.46,0:10:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎来到螯合乐园
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.25,0:10:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 美冬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.98,0:10:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经没有时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.07,0:10:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,灯花
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.51,0:10:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.29,0:10:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,等一切结束 大家能一起去游乐园吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.30,0:11:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要在这种地方 拼上性命呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.02,0:11:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,听不到谢谢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.33,0:11:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那阿丽娜我就回自己的画室了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.52,0:11:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,「回去」指的是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.38,0:11:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,灯花和音梦都有灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.05,0:11:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,所以阿丽娜加入了她们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.69,0:11:39.64,Default,,0,0,200,,但是 阿丽娜追求的艺术
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.64,0:11:44.27,Default,,0,0,200,,才不是和无知的人偶少女们过家家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.27,0:11:45.27,ObjectText,,0,0,0,,{\fn7945c739-da34-4855-ad19-aef0f03de57d\fs55\fsp25\fscx90\pos(960,650)}愚蠢的羊{\fsp0}群
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.60,0:11:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不过如果高潮要上演了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.76,0:11:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,能打电话告诉阿丽娜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.84,0:11:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.59,0:12:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,被前后夹击了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.82,0:12:04.58,ObjectText,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1660,670)\c&H2B241E&\3c&H707070&\bord2\b1}海盗船
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.71,0:12:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,那家伙 我记得是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.34,0:12:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,但是为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.73,0:12:33.48,ObjectText,,0,0,0,,{\c&H2B241E&\3c&H707070&\bord2\b1\pos(1768,748)}海盗船
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.85,0:12:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,天气会变得怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.62,0:12:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,预报说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.29,0:12:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这种时候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.17,0:12:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.94,0:12:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.36,0:12:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定会放晴的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.41,0:12:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.22,0:13:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,大家系好安全带了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.01,0:13:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,伴随着狂风骤雨 超级风暴前进方向朝东北偏移
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.02,0:13:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,风力持续增强并沿太平洋海岸移动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.55,0:13:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…只是猜测而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.27,0:13:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,魔女之夜也会出现在神滨市吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.37,0:13:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,诶？这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.13,0:13:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,魔女之夜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.16,0:13:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是 我们听说那家伙会出现在见泷原
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.19,0:13:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,既然Magius召唤了这附近的魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.95,0:13:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,魔女之夜或许也在其中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.34,0:13:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,无法否定这种可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.95,0:13:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,如果连那种东西都来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.55,0:13:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我们和神滨都完了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.40,0:14:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果是魔法少女
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.03,0:14:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,说不定这样糟糕的情况都能改变
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.55,0:14:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那么果然我成为魔法少女是一件好事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.99,0:14:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想这么认为
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.41,0:14:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不错的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.91,0:14:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,从这开始可不会轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.01,0:14:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,后面的两人也没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.91,0:14:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.48,0:14:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,那么我就做好被吊销驾照的觉悟冲进去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.42,0:15:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你在这种地方干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.47,0:15:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我想去那个城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.67,0:15:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,就凭你一个人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.59,0:15:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.71,0:15:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,即使如此 如果现在什么都做不到 我又会后悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.64,0:15:19.40,ObjectText,,0,0,0,,{\p1\move(1250,232,1250,450)\c&HF5FEFF&}m 0 0 l 470 0 470 300 0 300
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.64,0:15:19.40,ObjectText,,0,0,0,,{\c&H303835&\fncff0c41b-8180-4738-b962-625a148e246b\fs82\fscy120\fscx105\blur0.8\fsp20\move(1266,164,1266,382)}欢迎\n漂亮话少女
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.64,0:15:19.40,ObjectText,,0,0,0,,{\c&H515B58&\fncff0c41b-8180-4738-b962-625a148e246b\fs36\move(1266,348,1266,565)}你的愿望能拯救多少人呢\n你的愿望有过意义吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.97,0:15:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你认真的吗 看上去你没有强大到能独自一人扮演英雄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.95,0:15:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,只有我能拯救那些孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.53,0:15:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,难道你认识Magius的孩子们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.85,0:15:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你认识音梦她们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.23,0:15:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.78,0:15:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是希望她们的计划失败而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.79,0:15:42.30,ObjectText,,0,0,0,,{\fr-43\fax-0.6\fs40\fn7945c739-da34-4855-ad19-aef0f03de57d\fsp17\c&H9F9F9F&\pos(1574,404)}回想起祈愿与罪恶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.65,0:15:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那也可能是搞错了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.74,0:15:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 我必须去确认
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.02,0:15:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,靠这个移动会稍微方便点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.27,0:15:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.57,0:15:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,佐仓杏子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.97,0:15:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,环彩羽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.47,0:16:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,七海 前面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.39,0:16:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,焰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.39,0:16:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你们两个没事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.66,0:16:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那么接下来怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.75,0:17:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,目前为止都在计划之中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.39,0:17:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,顺利 顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.45,0:17:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,彩羽 听得见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.44,0:17:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,彩羽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.15,0:17:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,八千代 你在附近吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.61,0:17:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,对 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.44,0:17:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,看来没那么简单能进去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.48,0:17:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.12,0:17:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我去开门
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.93,0:17:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,冷静 你一个人太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.33,0:17:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,磨磨蹭蹭的话一个人都救不了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.41,0:17:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,既然我在 就由我来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.33,0:17:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这是只有我能做到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.73,0:17:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,会顺利吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.05,0:17:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这或许是我的任性
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.67,0:17:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,相信那孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.57,0:17:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,请开门
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.11,0:17:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,没听说这种命令
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.13,0:17:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在命令你们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.47,0:17:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,请快…赶快！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.47,0:18:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.61,0:18:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,环彩羽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.12,0:18:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.94,0:18:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.67,0:18:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会有人笨到正面突破啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.97,0:18:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,佐仓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.45,0:18:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然认同你的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.53,0:18:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,但这样会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.09,0:18:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我还没死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.24,0:18:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,因为佐仓你来救我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.45,0:18:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是说这种话的时候吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.61,0:18:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,暂时撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.53,0:18:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 笨蛋 你想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.63,0:18:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是为了仅仅一个愿望成为魔法少女的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.99,0:19:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我想知道愿望的去向
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.21,0:19:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然不知道你许了什么愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.79,0:19:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,但愿望的坟地可不是什么好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.71,0:19:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,请和我连携
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.93,0:19:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,仅凭我一个人无法做到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.56,0:19:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,赶快搞定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.91,0:19:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我也觉得
